Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me WeAreYoung release teaser video for 'Only I Love You' By KpopJoA 1 hour ago 2,887 152 0 0 Google+ Ballad duo WeAreYoung released their teaser video for " Only I Love You ".
The lyric teaser video features the two singers performing live playing on piano and guitar at various events. WeAreYoung's first single will be released on February 21.
